title: Mama Falafel
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Middle Eastern cuisine menu with a range of vegan choices including falafel in a wrap or pocket, falafel burger, quinoa chicpea, Israeli salad, tabouli, fries, juices, and 2 smoothies (lemon fresh & acai bomb). Fries and falafels are cooked in dedicated fryer without cross contamination. Falafel burger is cooked on separate grill from meatstuff. Note that honey is used in the dressing for wild rice salad, couscous salad; mayonaise in coleslaw salad, broccoli salad; the tzatziki dip and spinach and feta salad are not vegan.
